message.body: I got Kathy's birth day wrong it's today the 25th three days after Tony's.thought you'd like to know.
I know your appointment is Friday you might want to call them and ask if they can email you the new patient forms so you can start filling them out before the visit.
It can make it a little less stressful then trying to do it at the office
I asked they said I have to do it there
That's okay it was worth asking
